<mjml>
  <mj-head>
    <mj-preview>
      Your PoeticMetric free trial has ended, events will still be collected, upgrade now to access the reports. Check your e-mail for more
      information
    </mj-preview>

    <mj-attributes>
      <mj-button
          background-color="#3182CE"
          border-radius="6px"
          font-family="-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif"
          font-size="16px"
          font-weight="600"
      />

      <mj-text
          color="#2D3748"
          font-family="-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif"
          font-size="16px"
          font-weight="400"
          line-height="24px"
          padding-left="40px"
          padding-right="40px"
      />
    </mj-attributes>

    <mj-style inline="inline">
      a {
        font-weight: 700;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #3182CE;
      }
    </mj-style>
  </mj-head>

  <mj-body background-color="#F7FAFC">
    <mj-section>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-spacer height="20px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#EBF8FF" border-radius="8px 8px 0 0">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image
            width="200px"
            src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/698079/139349672-47706255-455f-4859-955c-2d1e927add90.png"
            align="center"
            alt="PoeticMetric Logo"
            href="{{.FrontendBaseUrl}}"
        />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" border-radius="0 0 6px 6px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text>
          <p>Greetings,</p>

          <p>
            We wanted to reach out to let you know that your <strong>30-day free trial of PoeticMetric has ended</strong>. We hope that
            you've been able to gain valuable insights into your website's traffic during your trial period.
          </p>

          <p>
            As your trial has ended, you will no longer have access to all of the features and benefits of PoeticMetric.
            <strong>
              However, we would like to inform you that your events will still be collected, but you will not be able to access the reports
              unless you upgrade to one of our paid plans.
            </strong>
            Our plans are designed to fit the needs of any organization and budget. You can find more information on our
            <a href="{{.FrontendBaseUrl}}/pricing">pricing page</a>
            .
          </p>

          <p>
            If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team. We're always here to help.
          </p>
        </mj-text>

        <mj-text>
          <p>Cheers,</p>

          <p>The PoeticMetric Team</p>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section padding-top="8px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text font-size="12px" align="center">Copyright Â© WebGazer, Inc.</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
